==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Solar parallax
<hw>Solar parallax</hw>. <def>The parallax of the sun, that is, the
angle subtended at the sun by the semidiameter of the earth. It is
8.80⟦prime⟧⟦prime⟧, and is the fundamental datum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Solary</ent>⟦br⟧
